<br>
Shamens are a chain class, and a priest, their ac cap is probably around 250 under that impressive 1250 ac.<br>
<br>
Plate tanks (war/pl/sk etc) are capped at 1200-1250, depending on who you ask.<br>
<br>
Magicians and all other int casters are capped around 800-900<br>
